@ inspironlaptop

Bando Shin Ke Chude Kata Bejanmar Bacha Karli Re ! Joyeeta Ke Toh Tor Baba Chodar Gusti Chude Chulke Pod Mere Suorer Chana Vikhirr Bacha Tairi Karlo ! Elika Magir Mon Kuttar Dhon ! Das Banchod Babu Toh Toke Upore Niche Pichane Samne Chude Taralo Sabjantu ! Sabjantu Vatbazer Pod Chete Dili Tao Ban Holi ! Joy Gandur Nunu Kha Harami !
